Description:
    Creates an AngularJS app with Bourbon, Neat and Bitters

Example:
    yo angular-bourbon [--coffee]

    This will create:
        Gruntfile.js
        bower.json

        app/index.html
        app/scripts/your-app-name-here.js
        app/scripts/controllers/main.js
        app/bower_components/angular/angular.js
        app/styles/main.css
        app/views/main.html

        test/lib/angular-mocks.js
        test/spec/controllers/main.js
